'''Lobosillo Solar Park''' is a 12.7  [[MW-peak]] [[photovoltaic]] [[power plant]] located in [[Lobosillo]], [[Murcia]], Spain, making it at the time the third largest photovoltaic (PV) power plant in the world.<ref name="pvresources">[http://www.pvresources.com/en/top50pv.php Large photovoltaic power plants]</ref> 

The plant was constructed by [[Ecostream]]<ref>http://www.ecostream.es</ref>  and uses [[Sputnik Engineering]]'s SolarMax<ref>http://www.solarmax.com</ref> [[solar inverter]]s .

It was opened for operation in September, 2007 <ref name="pvresources"/>

